ECC
Full form : The full form of ECC is ERP Central Component.
Definition : "It is the SAP system in which we use traditional databases like - Oracle, Sybase, DB2 etc.

Application Layer - ECC
Database Layer - Oracle , Sybase, DB2 etc."

Identification:
"a) In MARA table, the length of material number is 18.
b) Check the product version and database using  system-status.
C) The transaction codes XD01 and XK01 still exists."



SOH
Full form : The full form of SOH is SAP Business Suite on HANA

Definition : "In this system, only the database is HANA 
Application Layer - ECC
Database Layer - HANA"

Identification:

"a) In MARA table, the length of material number is 18.
b) Check the product version and database using  system-status.
C) The transaction codes XD01 and XK01 still exists."



S4H or S/4H.
The full form of S4H is SAP Business Suite for HANA
"In this system, the complete suite is in HANA.
Application Layer - HANA
Database Layer - HANA"
"a) In MARA table, the length of material number is 40.
b) Check the product version and database using  system-status.
C) The transaction code XD01 and XK01 are obsolete, it navigates to transaction code BP."


Brief Introduction to HANA
HANA - High Performance Analytic Appliance( Hardware + Software)
It uses in memory database technology which allows to process large amount of data in real time.
